tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE VirtualWorldEnvironmentData (
   data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   temperature FLOAT,
   humidity FLOAT,
   terrain_type VARCHAR(50),
   object_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE VirtualWorldData (
    world_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    world_name VARCHAR(255),
    terrain_type VARCHAR(100),
    climate VARCHAR(50),
    population INT
);

CREATE TABLE EnvironmentData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    latitude FLOAT,
    longitude FLOAT,
    temperature FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE VirtualObjects (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    color VARCHAR(20),
    size FLOAT,
    location_id INT REFERENCES Locations(id)
)

CREATE TABLE Locations (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    description TEXT,
    latitude FLOAT,
    longitude FLOAT,
    environment_id INT REFERENCES EnvironmentData(id)
)

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    location VARCHAR(255),
    interests VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE ar_vr_devices (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    device_name VARCHAR(100),
    vendor VARCHAR(100),
    resolution VARCHAR(20),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE Interactions (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  object_id INT,
  user_id INT,
  action VARCHAR(50),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Assets (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255),
  type VARCHAR(50),
  size VARCHAR(20),
  file_path VARCHAR(255)
);
